<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA52">
<l>niṟaṅkariyaṉ ceyya neṭumalarāṇ mārva</l>
<l>ṉaṟamperiya ṉāra taṟivār – maṟampurinta</l>
<l>vāḷarakkaṉ pōlvāṉai vāṉavarkōṉ ṟāṉattu</l>
<l>nīḷirukkaik kuyttā ṉeṟi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is black in colour, who has on [his] chest her of the big red [lotus] blossom,</l>
<l>who is great in Dharma – who are those that know it,</l>
<l>the path of him who sent the one resembling a Rākṣasa  with a sword, who committed braveries,</l>
<l>for a long stay at the site of the king of celestials?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
